title: Updated! Basketball Court! Dog Park!  Easy Access To Highways!
posting_body: ['Our one, two, and three bedroom apartments in West Lewisville, Texas, feature stylish and modern details you’ll love, such as granite countertops, wood-style flooring, and luxurious brushed nickel fixtures.', 'Stunning interiors are just the beginning here.', 'A few steps away from your front door, a world of amazing amenities awaits.', 'Within the community you’ll find two large swimming pools and a basketball court to keep you healthy and strong, a dog park for you and your pup, and much more.', 'Tucked away. . .', 'and worth the find!', "You'll know you've found the perfect home when you visit our community.", 'Easy access to I-35 and Highway 121, just minutes from Vista Ridge Mall and a quick 15 minute drive to DFW airport.', 'We offer you a convenient location for both work and play!', 'Please Call Desiree at', 'show contact info', 'Mention ad D 152', 'DASH Apartment Locators']
